homepage.ais_features.wifi.description.message: {aisSocket} is the easiest way to add a touch of intelligence to your home devices. The device runs on software, the sources of which and the compiled version are provided for free. So you have a choice of {moreWiFiDevices} devices, that you can connect to the gate in the same simple way as our Smart Socket.

homepage.ais_announcement_line_one.message: We automate your home by combining the advantages of local processing

homepage.ais_announcement_line_two.message: with connectivity to IoT cloud services.

homepage.ais_gate_description.message: The innovative gateway controls devices locally, ensuring instant response and privacy, and also plays multimedia and has more possibilities than competing solutions.

homepage.ais_one_gate_for_all_text.message: Many intelligent devices and one system to rule them all!
homepage.ais_one_gate_for_all_text.description: One gate to rule them all text

homepage.ais_project_people_info.message: Project created and sponsored by people - thank you!
homepage.ais_project_people_info.description: This project is sponsored by people info

homepage.ais_features.zigbee.description.message: With {aisZigbee} you can easily attach Zigbee devices to the gateway. More than {moreZigbeeDevices} are supported by the Zigbee2Mqtt software we provide on the gateway.

homepage.ais_features.ha.description.message: One of the components of the software delivered on the gateway is the {aisHomeAssistant} home automation system with installed and ready-to-use embedded {aisHomeAssistantIntegrations} integrations, and with the ability to add more than {moreHomeAssistantMoreIntegrations} that are supported and developed by the Home Assistant community.

homepage.ais_features.voice.description.message: We provide {aisVoiceCommands} (speech-to-text) and built-in commands on the gateway, so you can control attached devices using voice commands. Commands can be sent from the {aisVoiceCommandsWeb} browser application, the {aisVoiceCommandsMob} mobile application or the {aisVoiceCommandsRemote} remote control. You can also send commands from other systems / applications using {aisVoiceCommandsApi}. And define your own {aisVoiceCommandsCreate} commands.

homepage.ais_features.audio.description.message: We provide a built-in {aisAudioPlayer} audio player on the gateway, with which you can play hundreds of radio stations, podcasts, free audiobooks, free content from {aisAudioYouTube} and {aisAudioSpotify}. It is also possible to define your own additional audio content in {aisAudioPortal}.
